<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.5.2">
<l>tātaviḻ mallikai pulkivanta taṇmati yiṉiḷa vāṭaiyiṉṉē</l>
<l>yūtaiti ritantu ḻaṟiyuṇṇa vōrira vumuṟaṅ kēṉuṟaṅkum</l>
<l>pētaiyar pētaimai yāliruntu pēcilum pēcuka peyvaḷaiyār</l>
<l>kōtaina ṟumalar maṅkaimārvaṉ kuṟuṅkuṭik kēyeṉṉai yuyttiṭumiṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When the north wind in the cool moonlight which arrives having caressed</l>
<l rend="indent">the jasmine where pollen falls</l>
<l>[Seems] roused, thus whirling erratically [like] a tempest,</l>
<l rend="indent">I do not sleep for even one night!</l>
<l>Even if the foolish girls who sleep [well] sit and talk in foolishness,</l>
<l rend="indent">let [those] ladies [still] wearing bangles talk.</l>
<l>Make sure you take me to Kuṟuṅkuṭi of the one on whose chest</l>
<l rend="indent">is the lady with fragrant flowers in a garland.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
